title: BLACK & White PC Game files in SWEDISH
description:
The much loved game created by Lionhead Studios LTD, BLACK & WHITE, in Swedish!

These are only files you shall use to REPLACE your current installation of Black & White, so to play the game in Swedish, here is what you must do.

1: Get the game via a torrent, pirating, or installing it from a disc in whatever language accessile to you. English recommended though.

2: Extract all files into the Black & White Installation folder.

3: Play!

The game will now entirely be in Swedish, all texting and voices! This might render the game incompatible with the Creature Pack addon though. Updating it to 1.2 may still work, but I've yet to try it.

Now, this is intended mainly for people that understand and/or speak Swedish, and many Swedes have been longing to play the game in Swedish, and there is no way to get it in Swedish anymore, so I am providing a means for it.

Enjoy Swedish Good or EEEVIIIIL!
